People don't want to get screwed over. If you guarantee to people that there's no possibility they will get screwed over, it's incredible what they'll give you in return.

Nick Corrigan exploited this to disarm people on that one game show.

Amy Chua teaches this to her children: if they put in hard work -> success -> recognition. This fuels more hard work in a "virtuous circle".

How to use:
-sooth the fears of other people's wrt getting cucked
-acknowledge this fear in yourself, and try to suppress it
But what if cucking is actually happening?
-we live in a remarkably low-cucking society
-take the outside view on cucking
